sonusGatewaySignallingMIB.description: The MIB Module for IP Call Signal Channel Management.

sonusGwSigSrvTimerT301.name: sonusGwSigSrvTimerT301
sonusGwSigSrvTimerT301.description: This is the gateway to gateway call establishment timer T301 (in seconds). This value applies to all future GW-GW calls.

sonusGwSigSrvTimerT303.name: sonusGwSigSrvTimerT303
sonusGwSigSrvTimerT303.description: This is the gateway to gateway call setup timer T303 (in seconds). This value applies to all future GW-GW calls.

sonusGwSigTimerEstabish.name: sonusGwSigTimerEstabish
sonusGwSigTimerEstabish.description: This is the Gateway Signal Channel Establishment Timer (in seconds.) This value applies to all signal channels.

sonusGwSigTimerKeepalive.name: sonusGwSigTimerKeepalive
sonusGwSigTimerKeepalive.description: This is the Gateway Signal Channel Keepalive Timer (in seconds.) This value applies to all signal channels.

sonusGwSigAction.description: The action to be taken on the specified link.

sonusGwSigPortNum.description: TCP port number of Gateway Signal Listen Port (default is Sonus registered port 2569).

sonusGwSigPortInterface.description: The interface type of Gateway Signal Listen Port. This element select which gateway network interfaces to use for GW-GW signaling traffic. 'mgtnif' routes traffic over the gateway Managment ports. 'nif' routes traffic over one of the gateway PNS ports.
